name: Luxembourg part 2
description:
When the last expansion came the r/placeluxembourg came to the conclusion that their flag and primary part were stable and decided by choice of De_Nederbelg (Matthewvv) that they should expand east to make more Luxembourgish things.

Eventually Kademo15 designed:

On the left classic Luxembourgish Mostard.

On the right we build the famous luxembourgish cheese Kachk√©is. With it being accompanied with a piece of bread and a  dab of mostard.

Finaly on the bottom we see The Grand Duchess Charlotte Bridge also known as the Red Bridge due to it being red.

The Background is the background of the official coat of arms of Luxembourg.
